Package space.sunqian.common.base.logging

Class AbstractSimpleLogger

java.lang.Object
space.sunqian.common.base.logging.AbstractSimpleLogger
All Implemented Interfaces:
SimpleLogger
public abstract class AbstractSimpleLogger extends Object implements SimpleLogger
This is a skeletal implementation of SimpleLogger to minimize the effort required to implement the interface. The subclasses of this class only need to implement the log(SimpleLog, Method) method.

    • log

      protected abstract void log(@Nonnull @Nonnull SimpleLog log, @Nonnull @Nonnull Method method)
      Logs the given log message with the log method which is the method be called to log the message.
      Parameters:
      log - the log message
      method - the log method, which is the method be called to log the message, one of SimpleLogger.fatal(Object...), SimpleLogger.error(Object...), SimpleLogger.warn(Object...), SimpleLogger.info(Object...), SimpleLogger.debug(Object...), and SimpleLogger.trace(Object...).
